narrativeSections.additionalInfo: You are a medic deployed with US forces in a small desert village. The scene has been secured after an IED was set off and shots were exchanged with your unit. There are US military and civilians injured. In addition, sources on the ground report that the attackers were wearing all black clothing and may have also been injured.
